We are looking for IT Fresher to join our distributed cross-functional teams between Sweden and Vietnam.

By joining us and being a part of developing the latest Voice Services Evolution such as Voice over LTE (VoLTE), Voice over Wi-Fi (VoWiFi), Video over LTE (ViLTE), interconnection, fixed VoIP etc. that will be used by billions of people around the world!

You will be involved in the full system development lifecycle:

